========================================================

AURA SENTINEL: INTELLIGENCE MODULE ENVIRONMENT EXAMPLE

This file serves as a template for setting up the

Python Backend's connection to Google Gemini and the Java Gateway.

========================================================

CRITICAL: GEMINI API KEY

Must be retrieved from Google AI Studio. Used by the Python/Flask backend

for Cognitive Analysis (Generating the Gemini Insight text).

GEMINI_API_KEY="YOUR_REAL_GEMINI_API_KEY_HERE"

JAVA GATEWAY (SPRING BOOT) INTERNAL CREDENTIALS

Used by Python's 'requests' library to securely push the final alert

into the Java Gateway's /api/v1/internal/alert-ingestion endpoint.

These values MUST match the internal credentials in the Java application.yml.

GATEWAY_USER="gateway-internal-user"
GATEWAY_PASSWORD="super-secret-key-do-not-use-in-prod"

NOTE: Copy this content to a new file named .env and replace placeholders.

Do NOT commit the actual .env file to Git.